== 评价 ==
===票房===
影片于北美（美国和加拿大）地区与《{{le|光盲青春|Blinded by the Light (2019 film)}}》、《[[鲨海逃生|鲨海逃生]]》和《[[好小男孩|好小男孩]]》同日上映，首周末于2404家影院取得约500万美元的票房成绩<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/box-office-good-boys-angry-birds-2-1203300963/ |title=With Five More New Releases, Can Any Movie Break Through at the Box Office in August |last=Rubin |first=Rebecca |website=Variety |date=2019-08-13 |access-date=2019-08-13 |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815010151/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/box-office-good-boys-angry-birds-2-1203300963/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，加上120万首映票房（含20万周四晚点映票房），凭借350万的票房位列票房榜第11位<ref name="opening">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/good-boys-hobbs-shaw-47-meters-down-uncaged-scary-stories-weekend-box-office-1202669605/ |title=How Universal Is Reviving The R-Rated Comedy & Making 'Good Boys' Great At The B.O. With A $21M Opening |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |website=Deadline Hollywood |date=2019-08-18 |access-date=2019-08-18 |archive-date=2019-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816181043/https://deadline.com/2019/08/good-boys-hobbs-shaw-47-meters-down-uncaged-scary-stories-weekend-box-office-1202669605/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===专业评价===
据汇总媒体[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]，影评获166条评论，腐烂度49%，平均得分5.67/10。网站共识写道：“《伯纳黛特你去了哪》令人沮丧地证明了有才华的导演、畅销的原作和惊艳的剧组出来的效果，远低于三者单独效果的总和”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/whered_you_go_bernadette/|title=Where'd You Go, Bernadette (2019)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|access-date=2019-12-23|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202154208/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/whered_you_go_bernadette|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]评论有39条，平均分51/100，表示“褒贬不一或口碑平平”<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/whered-you-go-bernadette |title=Where'd You Go, Bernadette reviews |website=Metacritic |publisher=CBS Interactive |access-date=2019-08-23 |archive-date=2020-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230052855/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/whered-you-go-bernadette |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[影院评分|影院评分]]观众投票得分为“B”级（评级为A+到F）。{{le|PostTrak|PostTrak}}平均分3.5/5，“绝对推荐度”为60%<ref name="opening" />。

《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的{{le|理查德·罗珀|Richard Roeper}}打出2/4星的评分，认为影片无疑是“2019年最令人失望的电影之一，摄影风格扎实但简单，有问题的角色一大堆，消极得令人非常反感和沮丧，稍不留神就落入使人昏昏欲睡的老套路”<ref>{{cite web |last1=Roeper |first1=Richard |title=‘Where’d You Go, Bernadette’ focuses on a woman you wish would stay gone |url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/2019/8/14/20804487/whered-you-go-bernadette-review-movie-film-cate-blanchett-novel |website=Chicago Sun Times |accessdate=2021-02-25 |date=2019-08-14 |subscription=yes |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107230240/https://chicago.suntimes.com/2019/8/14/20804487/whered-you-go-bernadette-review-movie-film-cate-blanchett-novel |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[环球邮报|环球邮报]]》的巴瑞·赫兹（Barry Hertz）打出1/4星差评，表示“问题就在于，林克莱特在电影中深埋了许多隐喻，或者说影片遭到多次修改，打造出一个有见地、乃至说令人振奋的故事，讲述一位富有创造力的天才停止创作会发生的事情，这种修改做得似乎有点犹豫不决。然而，原作提出了很好的论点，那就是，对于某些艺术家来说，在前进的征途中选择离开也未尝不是一件坏事<ref>{{cite web |last1=Hertz |first1=Barry |title=The messy, tonally confusing Where’d You Go, Bernadette asks a question only Cate Blanchett obsessives will care to answer |url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/film/reviews/article-the-messy-tonally-confusing-whered-you-go-bernadette-asks-a/ |website=The Global and Mail |accessdate=2021-02-25 |date=2019-08-14 |subscription=yes |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806064052/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/film/reviews/article-the-messy-tonally-confusing-whered-you-go-bernadette-asks-a/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”[[香港01|香港01]]撰稿人寇斯珮认为，导演理查德·林克莱特过往的作品“善于发掘生活中的细节，呈现日常生活中被人忽略的细腻”，胜在真实，而本片改编自虚构小说，强烈的戏剧性质完全不是普通家庭主妇会遇到的人生课题，有一种一般人无法理解的情感，不那么容易让观众产生共鸣，这完全不符合导演的气质<ref>{{cite web |author1=寇斯珮 |title=【走佬阿媽．影評】天才主婦悲喜劇 童話色彩難服眾 |url=https://www.hk01.com/article/371318/ |website=香港01 |accessdate=2021-02-25 |date=2019-09-04}}</ref>。

